column2: SELECT u.up_name as [name],     &&& + cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,    dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,    p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, p.psfMag_u, p.psfMag_g,     p.psfMag_r, p.psfMag_i, p.psfMag_z, s.fiberMag_u, s.fiberMag_g, s.fiberMag_r, s.fiberMag_i, s.fiberMag_z, sl.specLineID FROM #x x, #upload u, PhotoTag p, SpecLineAll sl, SpecObjAll s WHERE u.up_id = x.up_id and x.objID=p.objID  ORDER BY x.up_id
